**************************************************************************
                                 ForFET

                    ReadME - ForFET - IIT Kharagpur
              Created by Antonio Anastasio Bruto da Costa
                  E-mail: bruto@cse.iitkgp.ernet.in

             Principal Investigator: Prof. Pallab Dasgupta

**************************************************************************

Use: For feature based formal analysis of Hybrid Auomata Models of AMS Circuits.

**************************************************************************

TO BUILD: Run the build-script 'build' in the folder forFET

Requires 
1. C, C++ compilers, lex, bison, JAVA, 32 bit C libraries
2. libglib2.0-dev, libjson-glib-dev
3. Untar spaceex into the root folder of the tool
4. Download dReach/dReal from https://github.com/dreal/dreal3/releases/tag/v3.16.06.02


**************************************************************************

TOOL USAGE:
Run using the followin syntax
 ./run

**************************************************************************

EXAMPLES: The new ForFET has a library consisting of a battery charger model, 
and a few features to start you out with.


